reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Surprised at how useful these became.
reviews.reviewText: Nice group of bags with a decent zipper. They were much smaller than I expected but were immediately useful in holding a variety of items. Socks, underwear, etc were kept from being all over the place in the suitcase. Shoes were kept from dirtying clothes. Somehow it just worked!

reviews.reviewText: Worked great for a recent trip overseas. Kept me organized with all the traveling. Good quality, didn't have any problems. Loved having a laundry bag.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: loved these packing cubes. they kept me very organized during my whole trip and they’re cute. good quality for price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars They're so TINY
reviews.reviewText: It's definitely only for carry-on luggage as you would need about three sets to fill a regular suitcase. The blue color is pretty, and they do hold a pretty good amount for a carry-on organization system, but I would need more than one package for my suitcase, so I feel the price is high for what you get. It would be worth the price if they had two of each of the large and the medium but honestly it would be far better if it contained 4 large and two medium because that is what is really needed to pack an average suitcase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Used these for traveling. Loved sectioning each item type. Much easier to sort through each day

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These are awesome travel partner!
reviews.reviewText: I travel a lot, and I used these packing cubes every time I travel. Very handy. Clothes are nicely packed and hardly wrinkle. You don't need to unpack. Just take the individual cubes and stick them in the drawer and you're done.
